reviews.text: We frequent this place regularly. They have really good food, good coffee, and very friendly people. It is a very calm atmosphere.

A very comfortable cafe for you to spend your afternoon. I have ordered the Bailey cappuccino and the Matcha mille crepe cake. The matcha mille crepe cake is one of the best cake I have tried.  You may sit there for the whole day in non-busy hour.  I highly recommend this place if you want to spend your holiday doing nothing.

It is very difficult to fine a good and decent cafe in MOS (a food desert LOL). This cafe is easy to find, just go out from the A1 MTR Exit and go direction to the mall, get 1 floor down and you will able to find their door. 

Ample place and tatami area is available.  However, no advance booking so you may have to go right at their opening hour (12pm?) if you don't want to wait so long. 

Their menu and food are great, most are Japanese dishes and many dessert choices ranging from waffle, soufflé, cakes etc. The coffee just so-so. 

Overall, highly recommend if you want to find a place for friend gathering and talking for a whole afternoon in MOS.

It's already 3rd time to try this store
1. standard of desserts can maintain well. it's strongly recommended to try it's Macha layered cake. sauce is good and texture is special. waffle is okay but more special is the sauce on top, with special pistachio.
2.  disappointment is the tatami corner is getting dirtier than before. no staff clean the trench area near the tall  glass curtain walls.
This place is so cute! Enjoyed the food and atmosphere! Friendly staff.

result.name: 屋子生活

reviews.text: 唔知係咪太耐冇幫襯，小弟都係鍾意以前嘅切件七味炸雞扒定食多d，而家嘅定食由炸雞扒變咗做炸雞球，肉質當然唔及炸雞扒(起碼雞扒冇咁多肥膏)，而且用嘅脆漿口感亦較為遜色；加上小弟鍾情於嗰度嘅飯素，然後問嗰度d staff攞多d,但係佢竟然話冇得加(以前係好豪爽咁俾的)。既然佢要加價又點解d食物同服務不進反退呢？咁我終於明白其他cm都話甜品好過主食lu~
We frequent this place regularly. They have really good food, good coffee, and very friendly people. It is a very calm atmosphere.
這裡的甜品比鹹食好味，午餐的選擇不太多，味道還可以。室內環境非常寬敞，有地台座位，很適合聚餐或獨自來放鬆。

烏溪沙という離れたところにあって遠く感じますが、MTR烏溪沙線を使えばあっという間。駅と隣接しているので、電車降りて徒歩3分で着きます。下手に都会のど真ん中の人が多いバカ高い店より相当居心地がいいです。店内は綺麗で、香港のレストランにしてはかなり広々ゆったりしています。座敷、ソファーと作りも日本的で、ゆっくり過ごすには香港で一番の穴場だと思います。
メニューは量が少ないけど、優しい味で日本食が恋しくなったら絶対おすすめ。デザートもすごく美味しいです。
ピークの時間を避ければ、大体入れます。

香港で生活していた中で、一番リピートした店でした。
這裏的環境非常舒適，如果你想在週末去一個沒那麼多人的地方， 讓自己可以放鬆一下的話，可以選擇到這裏，這裏的食品也很不錯。

result.name: Double Cove Place

reviews.text: Quiet place with some restaurants and a supermarket.  Locate near Lake Silver and Wu Kai Sha station.   Air is good and near sea.

Very quiet and pleasant environment. Uses natural lighting which feels quite nice. The modern design of the shopping mall plus the extraordinary WiFi makes it a great place. However, since it uses natural lighting, this place can get a bit stuffy on the top floor. There is not much variety of choices, as most shops are either restaurants or convenience
 stores.
All you would find here is restaurants after restaurants after restaurants. Plenty of food choices, but food quality's meh.
Nice, small and quiet shopping centre, not much to buy.  Clean and not many people, mainly residents.  Next to Lake Silver.  Lots of people bring their dogs around.  Lovely place
Romantic lighting at night. What a new era shopping mall for all age
